      <intermediateExchange id="6b6f27df-107c-599f-bcae-933bbe274f7b" unitId="77ae64fa-7e74-4252-9c3b-889c1cd20bfc" amount="0.399063145089249" sourceId="026b0ec7-c20a-43c6-806d-db5afdeb78e6" sourceYear="2000" sourceFirstAuthor="Gendorf" intermediateExchangeId="759b89bd-3aa6-42ad-b767-5bb9ef5d331d" activityLinkId="7a4d8ad6-3116-52f6-a46f-6b21b52d4df3">
        <name xml:lang="en">electricity, medium voltage</name>
        <unitName xml:lang="en">kWh</unitName>
        <comment xml:lang="en">EcoSpold01Location=UCTE
Calculated based on literature data published by the GENDORF Chemical Park. The factory produced an average of 2462760 tonnes of chemical substances (including intermediates) per year in the years 2015-2019. The average consumption of electricity in the years 2015-2019 was 982796751 kWh per year. This equals 0.39906 kWh/kg chemical produced.

References:
Chemiepark GENDORF, Umwelterklärung 2016, https://www.gendorf.de/Nachbarn/Umweltschutz/Industrie%20und%20Nachhaltigkeit
Chemiepark GENDORF, Umwelterklärung 2017, https://www.gendorf.de/Nachbarn/Umweltschutz/Industrie%20und%20Nachhaltigkeit
Chemiepark GENDORF, Umwelterklärung 2020, https://www.gendorf.de/Nachbarn/Umweltschutz/Industrie%20und%20Nachhaltigkeit</comment>
        <uncertainty>
          <lognormal meanValue="0.399063145089249" mu="-0.9186356162447631" variance="0.0006" varianceWithPedigreeUncertainty="0.08380000000000001"/>
          <pedigreeMatrix reliability="2" completeness="4" temporalCorrelation="5" geographicalCorrelation="4" furtherTechnologyCorrelation="4"/>
          <comment xml:lang="en">Estimation</comment>
        </uncertainty>
