        <unitName xml:lang="en">kg</unitName>
        <comment xml:lang="en">Calculation.  Calculated from the amount ethylene oxide and ethanol in the treated waste water assuming a carbon conversion of 96% for COD. The worst case scenario BOD=COD was used.  

